processes is two types 

1- for ground

2- background (deamon) in windos called service

NOTE : this deamon has its parent from whre we opend it 


if the systemd call it and i opend it from terminal

now if we terminat its parent (terminal ) it wont closed as its parent will be systemd

NOTE : when closing deamon the servece control will pass its parent to systemd to be its new parent

service can work localy or has port to send or recive from internet


