controlling perirety of process :


nice valiue :its a value to controle periorty of process in working

it start from -20  to 19

the defult (normal priority) is zero 

the highst priority is -20

the lowst prioroty is 19

NOTE :user can give lowst priority to the process but can't give higst priority to the process

NOTE: as root we can do evry thing

